A suspect was shot dead in Buruburu area on Friday and a revolver with six bullets found on him. The suspect was in the company of three others and were attacking motorists and pedestrians. The other accomplices escaped on foot after confrontation with the police and are being hunted. Elsewhere, police said dozens were left homeless in Kibera and Mukuru slums fires. "There were no injuries but many lost their property. The cause is unknown and probe ongoing," a police report states. Click here for the latest political news 